Descripción
EMS Prep Testing.
Pass Your EMS Exam On The First Attempt!
Whether you are testing for EMT, AEMT, or Paramedic we have the EMT practice tests and exams to help you pass the national registry with flying colors.
Our test prep tests follow the newest EMS Education Standards and were written by nationally certified EMTs and Paramedic instructors. The program allows you to instantly create your own practice tests with the same content as the national registry exam (NREMT). Studying with our practice questions, answers, and rationales will be essential to those who are taking the NREMT exam in the near future.
Actual exam questions and answers for self-study:
- Firefighter I & Il;
- IBSC FP-C®;
- NREMT® AEMT;
- NREMT® EMR;
- NREMT® EMT;
- NREMT® Paramedic.
Our app is a source of accurate exam questions and answers to help you pass your exam easily and quickly!
- Question content is constantly updated for FREE, so you don't have to worry about outdated questions.
Application features:
• Mode "Preparation"
• Mode "Exam"
• Mode "Marathon"
• Questions search
Advantages:
• The application does not require an Internet connection;
• Tests are always "Available".
• Many modes of work with tests.
This test simulator will help you prepare for the EMS exams.
The app is free with in-app purchases

EMS Prep Testing.
Pass Your EMS Exam On The First Attempt!
Whether you are testing for EMT, AEMT, or Paramedic we have the EMT practice tests and exams to help you pass the national registry with flying colors.
Our test prep tests follow the newest EMS Education Standards and were written by nationally certified EMTs and Paramedic instructors. The program allows you to instantly create your own practice tests with the same content as the national registry exam (NREMT). Studying with our practice questions, answers, and rationales will be essential to those who are taking the NREMT exam in the near future.
Actual exam questions and answers for self-study:
- Firefighter I & Il;
- IBSC FP-C®;
- NREMT® AEMT;
- NREMT® EMR;
- NREMT® EMT;
- NREMT® Paramedic.
Our app is a source of accurate exam questions and answers to help you pass your exam easily and quickly!
- Question content is constantly updated for FREE, so you don't have to worry about outdated questions.
Application features:
• Mode "Preparation"
• Mode "Exam"
• Mode "Marathon"
• Questions search
Advantages:
• The application does not require an Internet connection;
• Tests are always "Available".
• Many modes of work with tests.
This test simulator will help you prepare for the EMS exams.
The app is free with in-app purchases

Rreth këtij aplikacioni
arrow_forward
Aplikacioni Alcolizer OnSite Testing është mjeti ideal për Menaxherët e Sigurisë dhe Biznesit që kërkojnë rezultate në kohë reale, të përmirësuara celulare, të testeve të drogës dhe alkoolit sipas standardeve AS4760:2019.
Përdorimi i pajisjeve elektronike Alcolizer për të mbledhur rezultatet e testeve të alkoolit dhe drogës (AOD) nëpërmjet një aplikacioni do të thotë testim më i shpejtë, të dhëna të sigurta dhe aftësi për të sinkronizuar rezultatet me AlcoCONNECT™ Data Management. Kur kombinohet me AlcoCONNECT™ The Complete Solution, rezultatet e testit AOD mund të ruhen në mënyrë të sigurt në cloud dhe në majë të gishtave kur të keni nevojë.
Përditësuar më
1 shk 2023
Veglat
Siguria e të dhënave
arrow_forward
Siguria fillon me njohjen e mënyrës se si i mbledhin dhe i ndajnë zhvilluesit të dhënat e tua. Praktikat për privatësinë dhe sigurinë e të dhënave mund të variojnë bazuar në përdorimin, rajonin dhe moshën tënde. Këto informacione janë dhënë nga zhvilluesi dhe ato mund të përditësohen me kalimin e kohës.
Nuk ndahen të dhëna me palë të treta
Mëso më shumë për mënyrën se si e deklarojnë zhvilluesit ndarjen e të dhënave
Ky aplikacion mund të mbledhë këto lloje të dhënash
Informacionet personale, Shëndeti dhe fitnesi dhe Informacionet e aplikacioneve dhe cilësia e funksionimit

Mund të kërkosh që të dhënat të fshihen

arrow_forward
Edunext Technologies Pvt менен биргеликте Demo Testing App. Ltd. (http://www.edunexttechnologies.com) Индиянын эң акыркы өзгөчөлүктөрү бар мектептер үчүн биринчи Android колдонмосун ишке киргизди. Бул колдонмо ата-энелер, студенттер үчүн абдан пайдалуу колдонмо болуп саналат, студент жөнүндө маалымат алуу же жүктөө. Колдонмо мобилдик телефонго орнотулгандан кийин, студент, ата-эне студенттин же кызматкерлердин катышуусу, үй тапшырмасы, жыйынтыктар, циркулярлар, календарь, жыйымдар, китепкана транзакциялары, күнүмдүк эскертүүлөр, жаңылыктар, жетишкендиктер, талкуулар, почта ящиктери ж. Мектептин эң жакшы жери, ал мектептерди мобилдик SMS шлюздарынан бошотот, алар көбүнчө өзгөчө кырдаалдарда тумчугуп же жабылып калат. Колдонмонун дагы бир кызыктуу өзгөчөлүгү - акыркы жаңыртууга чейинки маалыматты мобилдик телефондо интернет байланышы жок болсо да көрүүгө болот.
Качан жаңырды
2023-ж., 24-ноя.
Окутуу
Маалыматтардын коопсуздугу
arrow_forward
Коопсуздук дегенде колдонмонун маалыматты кантип топтоп, аны үчүнчү тараптар менен кантип бөлүшө турганын түшүнүү керек. Маалыматтардын купуялыгы жана коопсуздугу колдонмоңуздун иштетилишине, жүргөн аймагыңызга жана курагыңызга жараша болот. Маалыматты иштеп чыгуучу берип, маал-маалы менен жаңырып турат.
Үчүнчү тараптар менен маалымат бөлүшүлбөйт
Иштеп чыгуучулар маалыматтардын бөлүшүлүшү жөнүндө кантип кабар берерин билип алыңыз
Маалымат топтолбойт

Acerca de esta app
arrow_forward
Explore su ADN con 23andMe. Descubra cómo su ADN lo conecta con más de 2000 regiones geográficas de todo el mundo. Obtenga información sobre su salud, rasgos y más.
• Ancestry + Traits Service incluye composición de ancestros, que cubre más de 2000 regiones geográficas, y más de 30 informes de rasgos, como la capacidad para igualar el tono musical, la aversión al sabor del cilantro y más.
 • DNA Relative Finder le permite optar por conectarse con otros clientes de 23andMe que comparten su ADN y sus antepasados.
 • Su árbol genealógico, creado automáticamente a partir de sus relaciones de ADN, le permite visualizar fácilmente cómo están todos relacionados.
• El servicio Health + Ancestry incluye todo en Ancestry + Traits Service más más de 65 informes genéticos adicionales, como peso genético, composición muscular y más.*
Ambos servicios requieren la compra de un kit y el envío de una muestra de saliva utilizando el kit de recolección provisto. Puede iniciar sesión en su cuenta para seguir el progreso de su muestra. Una vez que obtenga sus resultados, abra su aplicación para ver todos sus informes.
En la aplicación, también puede elegir responder preguntas de encuestas y participar en la investigación de 23andMe.
Nuestros rigurosos estándares aseguran un servicio de calidad.

Overview
Accessibility Testing & Reporting Tools that helps to reduce accessibilty testing efforts.
My end Goal is to reduce the testing efforts as much as possible and make the accessibility testing & reporting a smooth process.
Enhance your website's accessibility with the "Accessibility Testing Tools & Target Size Checker"
This powerful toolset empowers web developers, designers, and accessibility enthusiasts to create more inclusive and user-friendly websites.
Key Features:
1. ✅ Precise Target Size Checks: Ensure your website meets the critical "Target Size (Minimum) (Level AA)" accessibility guideline. Our extension provides accurate assessments, making certain that interactive elements on your website are large enough and easy to interact with, benefiting all users.
2. ✅ Accessibility Properties Uncovered: Inspects essential accessibility properties of UI elements, including aria-label, alt, text, hidden properties, title, and more, it will fasten the testing process.
3. ✅ HTML Inspector: You can easily copy the HTML code of any element on a web page just by hovering over it and use the HTML in your audit report.
4. ✅ Text Spacing (Level AA): We've added a powerful feature to help you check compliance with "WCAG SC 1.4.12: Text Spacing (Level AA)." With this feature, you can easily identify and rectify any text spacing issues.
Why Choose "Accessibility Tools & Target Size Checker"?
- You will get all accessibility tools that help to reduce testing efforts.
- User-friendly UI makes it easy to use
- Test Target Size (Minimum) (Level AA)
- Test Text Spacing (Level AA)
- Context Menu support
- Dynamic Content check
Upcoming Feature:
1) Automated issues
2) Automated Color Contrast Issues, Live fixing with recommended color.
3) Stay tuned for a game-changing feature! Soon, you'll be able to report accessibility issues directly from the web page itself. Say goodbye to manual data entry and copying/pasting into spreadsheets. Our extension will offer seamless reporting and the option to export issues to Excel or Google Sheets, streamlining your accessibility testing workflow.
Make web accessibility an integral part of your website development process. Join us in creating a web that's more inclusive and accessible to all users. 
Install the extension today and be part of the movement towards a more accessible online world.
For Accessibility Related issues/Suggestions, Please reach out to me on kingsaifi38@gmail.com

Overview
Gives you testing super powers with contextual notes, test suggestions, data generators and more.
Get testing superpowers with contextual notes, test suggestions, data generators and more. Taxi Test Assistant lives in your Chrome sidebar and helps testers build and test web applications. 
Contextual Notes:
Record a note related to a specific page and we'll bring it back the next time you're on a page with a similar URL.
Test Suggestions:
Get suggested tests relevant to what your browser window is showing. Take advantage of our huge library with everything from Security, Usability, Validation and more. Get detailed explanations, copy/paste data and step by step instructions on how to for test specific flaws.
Data Generators:
Generate data for personas, names, phone numbers and more. Choose from themes (like James Bond) and locales to get the right flavour.
Happy Testing!
Questions or feedback: email nate[at]testingtaxi.com or @natebosscher on Twitter

Mobile View: Web Testing & Device Simulator

Add to Chrome
Overview
Simulate any site on multiple devices simultaneously in a tab. Boost Development, UI/UX, & QA, with real-time responsive previews.
Embrace the future of Responsive Design - Now with localhost server & tailwind support!
-----
 Simultaneous Device Testing: View any website on multiple devices at the same time - live. 
 Development Mode: Works with your localhost served site without any additional setup.
 Hot Module Reloading: See code changes instantly across all devices with hot-reloading.
 Simplify your Workflow: Plugs directly into your existing workflow with no learning curve.
 Scroll & Navigation Synchronisation: Achieve synchronised actions like scrolling and navigating across all devices, for all websites.
 Full Web Compatibility: Navigate freely between any website or page - No limitations.
Who Should Use Mobile View?
-----
 Full-Stack and Front-end Developers.
 UX/UI Designers.
 Web Agencies & Freelancers.
 QA Engineers & Testers.
 Product Managers.
 Marketers.
 Anyone already using Polypane/Blisk/Responsively/Sizzy browsers... why download a whole browser when you can achieve the same thing in the browser your users use - Chrome!
Getting Started
-----
1) Install Mobile View from the Chrome Web Store.
2) Click the extension icon to activate it for the current tab.
3) The current site will update to a new look—courtesy of us!
4) Select devices and breakpoints for continuous live testing.
5) Preview the simulations! Continue developing and see your changes reflected in real time.
6) Browse Freely: Navigate to any page or site and continue your testing without disruptions.
Upcoming Features
-----
 Custom Breakpoints: Create and save custom screen dimensions tailored to your or your client’s needs.
 Device Skins: Activate or deactivate device skins for an authentic testing environment.
 Automated Breakpoints Cycling: Initiate a rotating breakpoints that cycles popular breakpoints sizes on a timed interval.
‍ User Profiles: Save different configurations of devices and breakpoints for future testing scenarios.
Recent Features
-----
 TailwindCSS Breakpoints added.
 Improved scroll synchronisation.
 Synchronised selection storage across sessions.
Support and Feedback 
-----
Questions or suggestions? Reach out to us at hello@mobileview.io. 
We value your feedback as we strive to make Mobile View even better.
Embrace the Future of Responsive Design Testing
-----
Stop switching. Start simulating. With Mobile View, seamlessly integrate cutting-edge testing capabilities into your existing workflow. Install today and revolutionise your development process!
1.3.0 Change log
-----
Features:
- Adds tailwindcss breakpoints to the extension.

I can test on multiple screen sizes inside the same browser tab.
Works great on my 27"! And I can simply rotate the iPad view to cover laptop screens as well.

Nov 15, 2023
By far and away the simplest solution I have yet found, and so nearly perfect. My only request would be to be able to add custom viewport sizes as none of the predefined ones hit my small or large breakpoints (Tailwind CSS defaults).
